        protected boolean isSupported(WebElement element)
        Description copied from class: Select
        The element will be used to create an instance of class Select or subclass.
        In the constructor Select.Select(WebElement) or constructor of subclass,
        this method will be called to test if the element is supported by this class Select or subclass.
